nodes.title: Dogs Tested to See Whether They’d Defend Owner During Home Invasion
nodes.tags: protection|"news"|"burglar"|"guard dog"|"confront"|"home invasion"|"inside edition"|"pets"|"dog test"|"beware of dog"|"cat-animals"|"ie investigates"|"intruder"|"dog"|"ie animal kingdom"
nodes.description: If a masked intruder broke into your home, would your dog attack or run away? Inside Edition put some dogs to the test to find out whether they would confront the burglar or wimp out. In a recent case, a robber kicked down the door of a home with two dogs, but instead of teaming up to take him down, the canines took off. Inside Edition tested Perry, a 5-year-old yellow Labrador. Her owner, Michelle Kellaher, loves her dog but wonders whether Perry would save her in an emergency.

nodes.title: The culture war between doctors and midwives, explained
nodes.tags: midwives|"propublica"|"medicine"|"doctors"|"Vox.com"|"vox"|"explain"|"explainer"|"nursing"|"birthing"|"childbirth"|"childcare"|"home births"|"home births vs hospital births"|"history"|"us history"|"medicine history"|"healthcare"|"neonatal care"|"neonatal healthcare"|"maternal mortality"|"infant mortality"|"pregnancy"|"in utero healthcare"|"babies"
nodes.description: A deeper look at history explains why when it comes to midwife use, the US falls behind other affluent countries.Read more in ProPublica's story here:https://www.propublica.org/article/midwives-study-maternal-neonatal-careAnd catch their latest in maternal mortality reporting here: https://www.propublica.org/series/lost-mothersDespite spending more per capita on health care than any other country, the U.S. has the highest rate of deaths related to pregnancy and childbirth in the industrialized world. But what makes maternal healthcare in other affluent countries look so different than the U.S.? Among other things, midwives. Midwives in the U.S. participate in less than 10 percent of births. But in Sweden, Denmark and France, they lead around three quarters of deliveries. In Great Britain, they deliver half of all babies, including all three of Kate Middleton’s. So if the midwifery model works for royal babies, why not our own? Check out the video above to find out how midwives have been at the center of a culture war that’s deeply rooted in race and class in America. nodes.title: 10 BONNES RAISONS DE NE PAS VISITER L’ AUSTRALIE | Lama Faché
nodes.tags: voyage|"australie"|"vacances"|"voyage pas cher"|"animaux"|"les animaux"|"top 10"|"top10"|"les 10"|"lama faché"|"listes"|"agence de voyage"|"sejour pas cher"|"sejour"|"voyage derniere minute"|"derniere minute"|"village vacances"|"sydney"|"voyage privé"|"incroyable"|"faits interessants"|"faits"|"bizarre"|"tendances"|"curiosités"|"le pire"|"le meilleur"|"top 5"|"10"
nodes.description:
Si l’on parle de qualité de vie et de beauté de paysages naturels, il va sans dire que l’Australie est le pays idéal. En effet, en raison de ses excellents indicateurs sur la qualité de vie, l’ONU a décerné à ce pays la deuxième position dans la liste des pays où il fait bon vivre, après la Norvège. Ce score est également dû aux indices spécifiques relatifs à l’éducation et à la moyenne d’âge élevée. Par ailleurs, l’Australie occupe une superficie d’environ 8 millions de km2, se positionnant ainsi comme le 6e plus grand pays du monde et la plus grande île habitée. Malgré cela, l’Australie comporte une faune et une flore particulièrement hostiles auxquelles vous n’êtes certainement pas habitué, et qui peuvent, dans certains cas, vous attaquer ou causer votre mort instantanée. C’est pourquoi, dans cette vidéo, nous vous présenterons 10 excellentes raisons de ne pas visiter l’Australie
.

nodes.description:
Kaif-e-Baharan - Episode 9 | HAR PAL GEO

Life of Kamran revolves around his mother Shiasta. His single parent is a heart patient, who had fixed his son’s marriage with her sister’s daughter, Seerat. But due to Seerat’s stray, she decides to marry Kamran with another niece Farwa; daughter from another sister. Despite knowing the lack of interest towards Kamran, Shaista is persistent to tie the knot of Kamran and Farwa.
Fatima soon-to-be Mrs. Shahnawaz plays a pivotal role in Kamran’s critical condition. Kamran couldn’t see Fatima’s face, but he could listen how the poor educated girl helped him; despite knowing that it could leave her in trouble. The humanistic value of Fatima impresses Kamran which results in their marriage. Kamran keeps her in a flat and plans to tell the hidden step and her pregnancy to Shaista, after the heart surgery. When Shaista is acquainted to this fact she does not accept Fatima as her daughter in law. 
Shahnawaz plays a ruthless ferocious game against the foes. Kamran finds out that his wife and son are dead, whereas Fatima is being told that she is now a widow of Kamran. 
What is the destiny of Kamran and Fatima? Will he always live like a widower? How will Fatima survive all alone with her son? How vulnerable a woman could be without a man?

nodes.title: 2018년 1월 29일 (월) 뉴스룸 다시보기 - DJ·노무현 뒷조사에 '대북 공작금'
nodes.tags: JTBC|"JTBC NEWS"|"뉴스룸"|"손석희"|"newsroom"|"sohnsukhee"|"뉴스룸 다시보기"|"뉴스룸 풀영상"|"뉴스 풀영상"|"뉴스 다시보기"|"JTBC LIVE"|"ㅓ슟"|"서지현 검사"|"서지현 jtbc 뉴스룸"
nodes.description:
1. DJ·노무현 뒷조사에 '대북 공작금' 2:11

이명박 정부 국정원이 '대북 공작금' 10억원을 사용해서 김대중, 노무현 전 대통령의 뒷조사를 했던 것으로 파악됐습니다. '데이비드슨'이라는 프로젝트명으로 김대중 전 대통령의 해외 비자금을 추적하고 '연어'라는 추가 프로젝트를 통해 노무현 전 대통령의 측근 비위를 캐려 한 건데 모두 사실이 아닌 것으로 드러났습니다.

2. 채용 비리…기관장 8명 즉시 해임 12:17

정부가 공공기관 채용비리를 전수 조사한 결과 대부분의 공공기관에서 채용과정에 문제가 있었던 것으로 드러났습니다. 정부는 채용비리에 연루된 현직 기관장 8명을 즉시 해임하고 임직원 189명은 일단 업무에서 배제한 뒤 수사결과에 따라 퇴출하기로 했습니다. 

3. 강원랜드 등 17곳 '부정 입사' 방치 16:37

강원랜드와 한국가스안전공사 등 17곳은 채용비리로 입사한 직원들에게 아무런 인사조치도 하지 않은 것으로 JTBC 취재결과 확인됐습니다. 소송당할 우려 때문이란 이유가 컸는데 관련법 개정이 시급하다는 지적입니다.

4. '농단 외면' 우병우에 8년형 구형 10:43

청와대 민정수석으로 일하면서도 최순실씨의 국정 농단을 막지 않은 혐의로 재판에 넘겨진 우병우씨에게 검찰이 징역 8년을 구형했습니다. 검찰은 우병우 전 수석이 자신의 업무를 외면해 국가 기능이 저해됐다고 밝혔고 우 전 수석은 표적 수사라고 주장했습니다.

5.  검사 성추행당했다…뉴스룸 출연 20:58

현직 여성 검사가 수 년 전 법무부 간부로부터 성추행을 당한 데 이어 사과를 요구했다가 인사 불이익을 당했다고 주장했습니다. 성추행 의혹을 제기한 해당 검사가 직접 뉴스룸에 출연합니다.

 6. 한파에 물가 급등…설 차례상 걱정 56:08

오늘(29일) 서울의 아침 기온 영하 12도로 한파가 다시 찾아왔습니다. 연일 이어지는 한파로 채소와 수산물 가격이 급등하면서 설 차례상 물가에 비상이 걸렸습니다.  

7. 슬픔도 아픔도 함께 나누는 밀양 1:03:25

이번 화재로 유가족과 시민들은 큰 슬픔에 빠졌습니다. 밀양시는 이달 말까지 추모 기간으로 선포했는데요. 사고 직후부터 오늘까지 나흘 간의 현장을 밀착카메라에 담았습니다.

nodes.title: GOD LEVEL Street Food in Mexico 2.0 | MONSTER BBQ Chicken + SUPER FAST Mexican ICE CREAM NINJA

nodes.description:
GOD LEVEL Street Food in MEXICO! We’re going for a full on Mexican street food tour outside of Oaxaca, Mexico, and discovering the most incredible SUPER FAST Mexican Ice cream NINJA, with the fastest skills, kind of like the Super Human Ice Cream Ninja of Mexico, along with amazing MONSTER BBQ Chicken with spicy salsa as well of DELICIOUS roast Lamb Barbacoa! ALL of the Best Mexican Street Food! We were really lucky to eat and try this and also to see the fast workers with GOD LEVEL skill make the ice cream afterwards!

In this street food tour vlog, we travel outside of Oaxaca city to Zachilla, to eat and try the best street food in Mexico and taste the world famous lamb barbacoa inside soft spicy tacos, as well as the most beautiful spicy BEST BBQ Chicken with tons of amazing spicy salsa. It was truly the best barbecue chicken! This was such a big adventure to go out and eat these amazing Mexican street foods.

The Best Street Food we found, was definitely the Mexican ice cream, which was made by the most amazing man, the Ice cream NINJA of Mexico! The ice cream was hand made and made so fast with amazing skills, EXTREMELY fast! 

You can watch our whole Mexican street food playlist here:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dHnqNOvDi44&list=PL903FZ5cNRa3m9fJD4DANjuJSS6z1f20R

The first thing we found in the local street food market outside of Oaxaca, Mexico, was the famous whole lamb barbacoa, it was incredibly juicy, soft, and covered with a slightly spicy chili sauce and served wrapped up in a tortilla  with lots of delicious salsa and guacamole. This is the beauty of Mexican street food, the amazing spicy and variation of dishes you can try in the local farmers markets like this one outside of Oaxaca, Mexico. All of the Mexican cuisine makes your mouth come alive , especially when you get to watch the cooking, in the outdoor kitchen AKA the street!

After that amazing Mexican barbacoa tacos, we continued exploring the farmers market  and found some delicious BBQ Chicken! It was truly MONSTER sized, flavoured with adobado sauce and lots of different spicy salsa. Watching it covered in the adobado marinade and sizzling on the grill was truly amazing! The smell combined with the juices bursting out of the meat was life changing! This is the true beauty of Mexican food, the spice, the atmosphere, and the variety of tons of street foods to try in Mexico!

After this, we found some world famous Mexican milk ice cream, known as Nieves, famous from Oaxaca. There were so many amazing flavours to try, but we went for the classic burnt milk flavour with “tuna”, also known as the fruit from the prickly pear cactus. This combo was very delicious and worth a try for sure! The most amazing thing about this was watching how fast they made the ice cream, with super human skill. They were truly fast workers, with GOD LEVEL skill!  They were some of the fastest workers I’ve ever seen! It was hand made ice cream and in order to freeze it, they had to spin the tub really fast. Watching them make it was amazing! The workers here at the ice cream shop had super human skill, spinning it so fast with incredible speed and precision! This was GOD LEVEL skill! It was so fun to watch!

The address for this farmers market is just a few KM outside of Oaxaca. It is in the town of Zachilla, which hosts the market every Thursday.

ABOUT THE FOOD RANGER 

My name is Trevor James and I'm a hungry traveler and Mandarin learner that's currently living in Chengdu, Szechuan, China, eating up as much delicious street food as I can . I enjoy tasting and documenting as many dishes as I can and I'm going to make videos for YOU along the way! Over the next few years, I'm going to travel around the world and document as much food as I can for you! I love delicious food! This channel will show you real Chinese food and real local food, not that stuff they serve in the Buzzfeed challenge. 

Thanks for watching, and please feel free to leave a comment, suggestion, or critique in the comments below! Please make sure to subscribe, it's the best way to keep my videos in your feed, and give me a thumbs up too if you liked this food video, thanks, I appreciate it! You could also share the video too if you liked it, that would be awesome.

nodes.description: My last stop in India is the city of Hyderabad and this city is the capital of southern India's Telangana state. This city is known for technology and many fantastic restaurants. In terms of food, this Indian city is most famous for its biryani or spicy rice. The biryani here is supposed to be zestier, more aromatic and deeper in flavor than other parts of India. I tried two of the most popular biryani places in Hyderabad but what surprised me the most was actually not just the delicious biryani but the incredible roast chicken kabab! Episode 2389:
-----------------------
Tappu Sena returns home without finding Pinku. Unfazed, they decide to find him at the earliest after taking a rest. Bhide, whose clothes are torn apart, has to offer explanation to Popatlal and Abdul. Will Tappu Sena find Pinku? Watch this episode to find out.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant.The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

I see you clicked on the show more button in the description. Excellent. Just as I planned. Intrigue plots  need a few things to work. No, not a perfect synergy of mystery, tension, great characterization and exciting action. All intrigue needs is a bunch of hooded dudes spouting cryptic nonsense at a screen showing the protagonists as they struggle in vain to figure out what is going on. What is really going on? What is the truth? The audience doesn’t know, but the greatest truth is neither does the author.
